quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  12,80,"Nuko bamaze gutakaza icyizere (cyo kuba bakwemererwa kugira undi basiga mu cyimbo cya Benjamini), bariherera bajya inama maze umukuru muri bo aravuga ati \"Ese ntimuzi ko so yagiranye na mwe isezerano mu izina rya Allah(ko muzamugarura), kandi na mbere mutarubahirije (ibyo mwasezeranye) kuri Yusufu? Bityo, sinzigera mva kuri ubu butaka (Misiri) keretse data abimpereye uburenganzira, cyangwa Allah agaca iteka (ryo kuhava mujyanye), kuko ari we Mukiranuzi usumba abandi"
  12,81,"(Ati) nimusubire kwa so mumubwire muti \"Dawe! Mu by’ukuri, umwana wawe yibye, kandi ibyo duhamya ni ibyo twabonye (kuko basanze igikombe cyabo mu mutwaro we). Kandi (igihe twaguhaga isezerano) ntitwari tuzi ibyihishe (ko aziba bakamusigarana)"
  12,82,"Unabaze (abatuye) umudugudu twari mo (mu Misiri) ndetse unabaze abagenzi twari kumwe; mu by’ukuri, turavuga ukuri"
  12,83,"(Yakobo) aravuga ati \"Ahubwo imitima yanyu yabashishikarije gukora ikibi (kuri Benjamini mukigeraho). Bityo, kwihangana ni byo byiza (kuri njye), hari ubwo Allah yazabangarurira bose. Mu by’ukuri, ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  12,84,"Nuko abatera umugongo aravuga ati \"Mbega agahinda ntewe (no kubura) Yusufu!\" Maze amaso ye arahuma kubera agahinda (ariko ariyumanganya) kandi ashenguka"
  12,85,"Baravuga bati \"Turahiye ku izina rya Allah! Ntuzigera ureka kwibuka Yusufu kugeza ubwo ushegeshwe n’agahinda cyangwa kakaguhitana"
  12,86,"(Yakobo) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, akababaro n'agahinda byanjye mbituye Allah. Kandi nzi ibyo mutazi kuri Allah"
  12,87,"(Ati) bana banjye! Nimujye (mu Misiri) mushakishe amakuru ya Yusufu na mwene nyina, kandi ntimutakaze icyizere ku mpuhwe za Allah. Mu by’ukuri, nta batakaza icyizere ku mpuhwe za Allah, usibye abantu b’abahakanyi"
  12,88,"Nuko binjiye iwe (kwa Yusufu) baravuga bati \"Yewe munyacyubahiro! Twe n’imiryango yacu twatewe n’amapfa, none twazanye amafaranga make cyane; bityo dupimire utwuzurize (nk’ibyo waduhaye), kandi udufashe. Mu by’ukuri, abagiraneza\". Allah agororera"
  12,89,"Aravuga ati \"Ese muribuka ibyo mwakoreye Yusufu na mwene nyina, igihe mwari injiji (mutazi ingaruka zabyo)"
  12,90,"Baravuga bati \"Ese ni wowe Yusufu?\" Ati \"Ni njye Yusufu, n'uyu (Benjamini) ni mwene mama. Rwose, Allah yatugiriye neza. Mu by’ukuri, utinya (Allah) akanihangana, Allah ntaburizamo ibihembo by'abakora ibyiza"
  12,91,"Baravuga bati \"Turahiye ku izina rya Allah, rwose Allah yarakuturutishije, kandi mu by’ukuri, turi abanyamakosa"
  12,92,"Aravuga ati \"Uyu munsi ntawe ubaveba; Allah abababarire, kandi ni we Munyempuhwe usumba abandi"
  12,93,"Nimujyane iyi kanzu yanjye muyishyire mu buranga bwa data, arahita ahumuka, kandi munzanire umuryango wanyu wose"